LINUX ADVANTAGES
Open Source: Source code is functional as it is an open-source system. The operating system is customizable for students of programming. The user can contribute, alter, and improve the code as per their use.
Security: Security comes first in IT. Linux offers such security reasons that it is a promising option for developers. Linux is less vulnerable than other OS. 
Free to use: Linux is free to use is no need to buy a special license. We can get it under a General Public license. One needs to pay a high amount for other OS licenses.
GUI: Although Linux is a command-line operating system but provides a Graphical User Interface or GUI like Windows.

